<sect2>
<title>Differences Between Specified Rights and Rights That Are Set
 </title>
<para> After setting trustee rights in a directory or file in the Gateway
volume, you  may find that the rights indicated in the trustee list are different
from the ones  that you set. This discrepancy occurs because of differences in NetWare and
DCE specifications  for rights definitions. As a result, the rights that are
set may differ  somewhat from the rights that are specified.
